<plot>Madeleine Severn (Janet McTeer) is a teacher and a virgin in a small town searching for Mr. Right. She falls in love with Bernard (Clive Wood), a fellow teacher but is being stalked by Paul (Johnny Lee Miller), a student. Is he the serial killer on the loose in London and who will be his next victim? The tension mounts in this murder mystery with a real twist in its tail.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?133047</url></doc>
